## Constraints

### Use

- Presigned URL upload — client → storage direct
- `CryptoService.encryptDocument` / decrypt — per-document DEK
- DocumentAccessGrant ayrı model — case access ≠ doc access
- Download presigned TTL 5 dk
- DocumentVersion append-only
- Async ClamAV worker — sync scan yok
- `@RequirePolicy` + DocumentPolicyService tüm download'larda

### Avoid

- Backend file relay upload/download
- Case visibility = document visibility
- Encryption "later" skip
- Sync ClamAV on request path
- Grant bypass for holding-level roles
- document_versions UPDATE (yeni versiyon = yeni kayıt)

